5. ✅ Accesses the header data through the span
6. ✅ Uses `binary_stream`'s `span()` method for zero-copy operations (second version)

Both implementations satisfy the exam requirements, with the second version being more aligned with the specification's emphasis on using `binary_stream`'s zero-copy operations.

